title: Dhokha Dhadi Song ft. Shahid Kapoor & Sonakshi Sinha - R...R
description:
Check out the sizzling chemistry of Shahid Kapoor & Sonakshi Sinha is this romantic song 'Dhokha Dhadi' from R...Rajkumar. The song is sung by Arijit Singh & Palak Muchhal.

Music: Pritam
Lyrics: Nilesh Mishra & Swanand Kirkire

Eros International & Next Gen Films presents 'R...Rajkumar' a film directed by Prabhu Dheva featuring Shahid Kapoor & Sonakshi Sinha in the lead roles. The film is produced by Sunil Lulla & Viki Rajani.

R...Rajkumar releases in theatres on 6th December, 2013.
